# Search an area for a location or object described in natural language.
# confidence_threshold: minimum match confidence to report a result (0.0-1.0)
# time_limit_sec: maximum task duration in seconds (0 = no limit)

# Goal
string query
geometry_msgs/Polygon search_area
float32 min_altitude_agl
float32 max_altitude_agl
float32 min_flight_speed
float32 max_flight_speed
float32 time_limit_sec
float32 confidence_threshold
---
# Result
bool success
string message
geometry_msgs/Pose found_pose
float32 confidence
---
# Feedback
string status
float32 progress
float32 best_confidence_so_far
geometry_msgs/Point current_position
